                        <head><hi rend="italic">Minister <persName type="from">Russell</persName> to
                                the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss></hi>.</head>
                        <opener><seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg></opener>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Caracas</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1906-02-06"><hi rend="italic">February 6,
                                1906</hi></date>.</dateline></opener>
                        <p>(Mr. Russell reports that on the 1st of February Venezuela named a
                            plenipotentiary to Colombia.)</p>
